{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Method","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Glossary/Method","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary\">MDN Web Docs Glossary</a>\n\n  <ul>\n   <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Function\">function</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Object\">object</a></li>\n   <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/property\">property <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Static_method\">static method <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  </ul>\n </li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Functions/Method_definitions\">Defining a method in JavaScript</a></li>\n</ul>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>메소드(<strong>method)</strong>는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Object\">객체</a>의&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/property\">속성 <small>(en-US)</small></a>인&nbsp;<a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Function\">함수</a>이다. 두 가지 종류의 메소드가 있다.&nbsp;객체 인스턴스에 의해 수행되는 태스크에 내장된 인스턴스 메소드&nbsp;또는&nbsp;오브젝트 생성자에서 직접 호출되는 태스크인 <em><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Static_method\">정적 메소드 <small>(en-US)</small></a></em>가 여기에 해당된다.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>참고:</strong> 자바스크립트 함수에서 그 자체는 객체이므로, 그런 맥락에서 메소드는 실제로 함수에 대한 객체 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Object_reference\">참조</a>인 것이다.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"더_알아보기","title":"더 알아보기","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"이것에_대해_알아보기","title":"이것에 대해 알아보기","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Wikipedia의 <a title=\"Method (computer programming)\" href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/Method_(computer_programming)\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Method (computer programming)</a>&nbsp;</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Functions/Method_definitions\">JavaScrip에서 메소드의 정의</a>&nbsp;(comparison of the traditional syntax and the new shorthand)</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"기술적_참조","title":"기술적 참조","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference\">List of JavaScript built-in methods</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"더 알아보기","id":"더_알아보기"}],"summary":"메소드(method)는 객체의 속성 (en-US)인 함수이다. 두 가지 종류의 메소드가 있다. 객체 인스턴스에 의해 수행되는 태스크에 내장된 인스턴스 메소드 또는 오브젝트 생성자에서 직접 호출되는 태스크인 정적 메소드 (en-US)가 여기에 해당된다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Method","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Método","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Méthode","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Method (メソッド)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Метод","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Method","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/glossary/method","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/glossary/method/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Glossary","title":"용어 사전"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Glossary/Method","title":"Method"}],"pageTitle":"Method - 용어 사전 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}